five years, all the way back

00:27:58.950 --> 00:28:01.290 align:middle line:84%
to the point that the
device was turned on.

00:28:01.290 --> 00:28:03.910 align:middle line:84%
But they can't go earlier
than that because of the fact

00:28:03.910 --> 00:28:08.100 align:middle line:84%
