earlier than that.

00:28:08.100 --> 00:28:10.340 align:middle line:84%
That means that--
and it doesn't matter

00:28:10.340 --> 00:28:12.690 align:middle line:84%
what particular
mechanism that you use,

00:28:12.690 --> 00:28:13.700 align:middle line:90%
I mean I'm using light.

00:28:13.700 --> 00:28:15.110 align:middle line:90%
That was my major breakthrough.

00:28:15.110 --> 00:28:17.380 align:middle line:84%
But any other way in
which you would do it,

00:28:17.380 --> 00:28:19.870 align:middle line:84%
it would be the device
that's causing the effect.

00:28:19.870 --> 00:28:22.035 align:middle line:84%
That means that since
we haven't develop it.

00:28:22.035 --> 00:28:23.660 align:middle line:10%
And, in fact, this
answers the question

00:28:23.660 --> 00:28:26.930 align:middle line:10%
